		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You touch a willing creature, crying out for all afflictions to be driven and cast out of them.</em></p><p><strong>Healing</strong></p><p>You remove debilitating effects from the target. You remove:</p><ul><li>One level of &amp;reference[exhaustion],</li><li>One &amp;reference[disease],</li><li>The &amp;reference[blinded], &amp;reference[dazed], &amp;reference[deafened], &amp;reference[drained], &amp;reference[paralyzed], &amp;reference[stunned], &amp;reference[poisoned], and &amp;reference[weakened] conditions.</li></ul><p><em>This spell cannot remove a condition caused by a &amp;reference[cursed]{curse} or another condition not listed (eg. a version of &amp;reference[frightened] that causes creatures to also be &amp;reference[weakened]).</em></p>",
